data.description: This stunning 26-acre property boasts a spacious porch with ceiling fans, perfect for enjoying those Texas sunsets. Located just minutes from the picturesque Sam Rayburn Lake, outdoor enthusiasts will delight in the convenience of Hanks Creek Park, only 5 miles away. This park offers a boat ramp, beach area, and more for endless recreation. The majority of this expansive property is densely wooded, ensuring your privacy and a true connection with nature. You'll even find a tranquil pond right on the grounds, creating a serene atmosphere for relaxation and reflection. The property backs up to the core of the engineer forest, providing additional seclusion and a breathtaking natural backdrop. Inside, the home offers 5 bedrooms, providing ample space for family and guests. Additionally, there's a dedicated office space, perfect for remote work or study. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a slice of paradise with the perfect blend of comfort and natural beauty.
